T1  - Mobile Pastoralists in the Logone Floodplain Distribute Themselves in an Ideal Free Distribution
AU  - Moritz, Mark
AU  - Hamilton, Ian M
AU  - Chen, Yu-Jen
AU  - Scholte, Paul
JF  - Current Anthropology
VL  - 55
IS  - 1
Y1  - 2014-02-01
DA  - Feb 2014
